title: CREATE_DUI
content:
0x23EAF899// CreateDui
long CREATE_DUI(char* url, int width, int height);Parameters:url: The initial URL to load in the browser.width: The width of the backing surface.height: The height of the backing surface.Returns: A DUI object.Creates a DUI browser. This can be used to draw on a runtime texture using CREATE_RUNTIME_TEXTURE_FROM_DUI_HANDLE.
